  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Lech and Residenz Chesa Rosa are located just a short walk to the resort centre and ski lifts. Rooms and facilities are located across both of the buildings. Each houses their own leisure area, where you can relax after your day exploring the vast Arlberg ski area. The lounge area with open fireplace, is great for relaxing with a pre-dinner glass of wine. And make sure you try out one of owner Andreas’ famous cocktails in the bar.</p>]]></description>
